        "product_description": {
            "value": "The blade of the dagger has been constructed from 440 Stainless Steel. An acid etched design decorates the top of the dagger. The dagger comes sharpened. \r\n<br><br>\r\nThe scabbard features a beautifully colored picture of a wolf pack. The handle features a wolf against an American Flag. The pommel of the dagger is a steel wolf head. This is the American Flag Wolf Fantasy Dagger With Sheath. The handle features the same image as the scabbard. The pommel of the dagger is a wolf head. These steel daggers are sure to be an instant center piece to any collection. \r\n<br><br>\r\nThe beautiful 7\" blade is crafted from high quality 440 stainless steel, and has an intricate inlaid design on the blade flat. The scabbard shows a beautiful image of a wolf pack, set against a dark blue and black background. \r\n<br><br>\r\nThe blade fits snug in the sheath, and slides smoothly and securely. The handle of the blade features the same image as the sheath. The pommel of the handle features a wolf head figure, and the guard is made of sturdy steel as well.",
